main_body:
Articles 1 and 2 shall not apply to the following categories of passenger cars:
(a) cars purchased for resale, hire or lease;
(b) cars used for transportation of passengers for a fee, including taxi services;
(c) cars used for the provision of transportation of goods;
(d) cars used for the provision of driving lessons;
(e) cars used for the provision of guard services;
(f) cars used as emergency vehicles;
(g) cars used as car sales demonstration vehicles.
